description:
Captain America's oldest enemy got murdered, but the star-spangled Avenger has to discover, that this murder is only a piece of a bigger, mysterious plan. Hunted by images of a past, which isn't his own, Captain America has to disarm bombs, which are scattered around the whole world, and has to find an incomplete Cosmic Cube - a weapon, which would be mighty enough to change reality!

Collects Captain America (Vol. 5) #1 - 7
name: Vol. 44 - Captain America - Wintersoldat

Jesus returns! Yes, classic 2000 AD artist Jesus Redondo returns for a special three-part Tharg’s 3riller story in 2000 AD Prog 1856, which is out on Wednesday 30th October and continues the fresh new stories ideal for new readers – including work from Al Ewing (Mighty Avengers), INJ Culbard (New Deadwardians), Ian Edington (Hinterkind), and Pat Mills (Marshal Law).

In this actionous volume:

-Alfred helps Batman in fighting crime, more than usual!

-Bane wants to beat Batman to a pulp, again!

-Batsy teams up with Catwoman to fight against her impersonator!

-Joker steals Batmans thunder, by making his own personalized vehicle!

-Riddler aims to find out whose face is behind the mask of the crusader who has a cape!

-Batgirl makes her first appearance in the comic series!
